condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :SCHEDULE 2. Section I. A.3 (a) | Description :The Borrower shall, not later than March 31, 2015, establish andmaintain throughout the period of implementation of the Project:(a) a Quality Improvement Plans Review Committee (QIPRC) withcomposition, terms of reference and resources acceptable to the Bank to review and approve Quality Improvement and MaintenancePlans submitted by Beneficiaries; | Due Date :31-Mar-2015

Finance Agreement :SCHEDULE 2. Section I. A.3 (b) | Description :The Borrower shall, not later than March 31, 2015, establish andmaintain throughout the period of implementation of the Project:(b) an Executive Accreditation Committee (EAC) with composition,terms of reference and resources acceptable to the Bank responsible, inter alia, to provide certificates of Accreditation toBeneficiaries that satisfactorily implement their QIMP. | Due Date :31-Mar-2015

Finance Agreement :SCHEDULE 2. Section I. A.4 (a) | Description :The Borrower shall, through MoHP, and after consultation with theBank, no later than March 31, 2015, prepare, adopt, and thereafter implement an Operational Manual, in a manner and substancesatisfactory to the World Bank. | Due Date :31-Mar-2015

Finance Agreement :SCHEDULE 2. Section I.B | Description :The Borrower shall engage, and thereafter maintain, throughout the periodof Project implementation, an External Technical Auditor under terms of reference approved by the World Bank, to design averification scheme and to supervise its implementation for the purpose of certifying compliance with the conditions set out inSection IV.B.2 (b) of Schedule 2 of the Loan Agreement. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Withdrawal ConditionSCHEDULE 2. Section IV.B.2 (a). i | Description :No expenditures shall be eligible forfinancing under Category 1 unless the pertinent Beneficiary has been preselected to participate in the Project on the basis of atargeting system acceptable to the Bank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Withdrawal ConditionSCHEDULE 2. Section IV.B.2 (a). ii | Description :No expenditures shall be eligible forfinancing ... under Category 1 unless the Beneficiary has carried out a self-assessment in accordance with ISQUA standards, anddeveloped a QIMP, in form and substance satisfactory to the Bank, for the improvement of the quality of its services and andmaintenance of its standards. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Withdrawal ConditionSCHEDULE 2. Section IV.B.2 (a). iii | Description :No expenditures shall be eligible forfinancing ... under Category 1 unless. said expenditures shall have been incurred for Accreditation Cost under part 1 of theproject, provided, however, that such expenditures shall not exceed US$ 70,000 for a family health care unit or center, establishedfor each Beneficiary for implementing its QIMP. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Withdrawal ConditionSCHEDULE 2. Section IV.B.2 (b) | Description :The Bank shall have received from theBorrower, through MoHP, verification certificates issued by the External Technical Auditor together with other supportingdocuments, in form and substance acceptable to the Bank, evidencing completion of the actions set out. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS
